title: 09/07:Start or Sit (NFC); ATL-PHI Recap (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
We begin with our thoughts on ATL-PHI at the top of the show. Are we concerned about Matt Ryan or Devonta Freeman going forward? Are Carson Wentz and Calvin Ridley droppable? ... Another Le'Veon Bell Watch (11:40), discussing the stud NYG players in their tough Week 1 matchup (13:04), Jamaal Williams is our Start of the Week (20:00) and we play Beat the Waiver Wire (23:20) to get you ahead of the game ... JAC-NYG (29:30), SF-MIN (33:40), NYJ-DET (39:15), TB-NO (44:46), DAL-CAR (49:21), WAS-ARI (53:40), GB-CHI (59:00) ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
